1999_July 8 

This marvelous show lasted eleven years. I wish it were still on. If you
were fed up with preachy, annoying treacle like the Cosby show (or any of
dozens of others), this was the antidote. There aren't enough like it.<br /><br />On the typical moralizing television &quot;sitcom&quot; the situation is always
(underlying) serious but never hopeless. The Bundy family's situation was
the opposite...
